message.body: @Equava Valid inputs are A, B, Z, L, R, Start, CUp, CDown, CLeft, CRight (C buttons), DUp, DDown, DLeft, DRight (D-Pad, unused in most games), Up, Down, Left and Right (Analog stick, used in almost every game as the standard movement input). Typos
